description:
It's the finale of our Duskhollow PD special and our team has 24 hours to crack the case!


Archie's investigations begin at the library, Emma is a proud mentor, Gabrielle Schreiber goes for coffee and Detective Sergeant Carl Husselback is questioning his life choices.


Thanks to this week's Patrons: Link Sandblom, Sindre Sareide, Retro Seamstress, Nick Mikoleit, Tasha, Msharki3, Alex K., Breanne A., Ashley Cecere, Emilia Williamson, Catherine White, aimsme, Hannah LaPlante, Sea, Britt & Astrid, juicysushi, Ferynn, Dean Winchester,Jessica Wells, Molly W


If you would like to join them, be sure to visit www.patreon.com/rustyquill


Edited this week by Michelle O'Toole, Tessa Vroom & Alexander J Newall.


In this episode, we used The Cthulhu Hack created by Paul Baldowski, to find out more or support Paul, head to:
